                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>For documentation on the efforts of Roosevelt and Churchill, before the First
                    Quebec Conference, to bring about a meeting with Stalin, see <ref
                        target="frus1943CairoTehran#pg_3">
                        <hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, The Conferences at Cairo and
                        Tehran, 1943, pp. 3</ref>–<ref target="frus1943CairoTehran#pg_20">20</ref>.
                    With respect to Anglo-American consultation with the Soviet Union in the period
                    before the Quebec Conference concerning the situation in Italy, see <ref
                        target="frus1943v02#pg_335">
                        <hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, 1943, vol. II, pp. 335</ref>, <ref
                        target="frus1943v02#pg_340">340</ref>–<ref target="frus1943v02#pg_350"
                        >350</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
